用什么metric表示advertising的impact
对于大型商户和小型local的商户，你的metric会有什么不同

对于大型商户和小型local的商户，你的metric会有什么不同
For large size business, like automobile sometime cares more about brand awareness, therefore, total_reached users should be a more meaningful metrics for this kind of merchant.
For small business, they cares more about ROI because the limited scope. Therefore, ROI or avg_user_per_ad should be more userful for them. 一亩-三分-地，独家发布

Additional suggestion, we can purge ads that had low ROI and low user spending and start help user do A/B test on factors that driver high ROI.

